{
  "stem": "3631.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if I go through the list, there are 30 or 40 names that I-- that I recognize, but--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she helped in the sick bay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She would walk in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would try to get food and-- and medicines for the sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she worked in this field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know whether I mentioned it, that-- I think it was in February-- that a transport of 200 people or so came in these frozen-- frozen cattle cars when the east camps were liquidated-- about two cars, I think-- that were going all over the country.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No concentration camp wanted to let them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was-- finally came to Brunnlitz I think they were for two weeks-- a week or two weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These cattle cars, in bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and Schindler ordered to let them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I understand, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Schindler wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Schindler called her husband, wherever he was, and he gave an order to let them in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We could not even open the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had to be-- we had to have torches to open them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And many of them were-- were just dead already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were-- they were frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And whoever could get them-- [INAUDIBLE] out, there were maybe 100 or 120 that we took in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they had to nourish them, and to bring them back to health.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
